author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Aboitiz Equity Ventures Inc Says Consortium Submits Proposal To Department Of Transportation

organizations.name: brief-aboitiz equity ventures inc says consortium

text:
Feb 13 (Reuters) - Aboitiz Equity Ventures Inc:
* NAIA CONSORTIUM SUBMITS PROPOSAL TO DEPARTMENT OF TRANSPORTATION REGARDING NINOY AQUINO INTERNATIONAL AIRPORT (NAIA)
* 7 PARTNERS SIGNED MEMORANDUM OF AGREEMENT FORMALIZING NAIA CONSORTIUM
* NAIA PROJECT ESTIMATED TO COST UP TO 350 BILLION PESOS OVER LIFE OF CONCESSION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
